how to use:
1.  make
2. run ./tank

help:
Player1's Key:
w-----------UP
a-----------LEFT
s-----------DOWN
d-----------RIGHT
J-----------FIRE

Player2's Key:
KEY UP------UP
KEY LEFT---LEFT
KEY RIGHT--RIGHT
KEY DOWN--DOWN
Del----------FIRE


